{"tid":2070641,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【美股悲劇】玩期權誤以為輸569萬　美年輕散戶自尋短見","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T12:19:33.000Z","uid":53433,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41a2b46b88b2891df8cffd0b6a19f22e4fa51b75","tid":2070641,"uid":53433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:09:08.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，由於疫情讓許多人留在家中，加上一些網上券商大削手續費，讓美國掀起「炒股潮」，許多年輕散戶投身「股海」，惟他們對投資工具可能一知半解，又大膽進取，最近就有20歲大學生疑似投資失利而自尋短見。<br />\n報道指出，網絡券商Robinhood表示，正在審查其選擇權交易產品。此前有消息指，該平台有客戶在使用APP交易選擇權後，疑似誤認自己輸了超過73萬美元(約569萬港元)而自尋短見。<br />\nSullimar Capital分析師Bill Brewster日前表示，他的表弟Alexander Kearns是個20歲的大學生，在疫情期間投身「股海」，惟最近離開了人世。<br />\nKearns在遺書上稱，Robinhood害死了他，因Kearns在Robinhood帳戶的狀態中顯示，他在交易中賠了73萬美元，而Kearns認為，他選擇的是虧損「有限」的期權交易，不知道為何會輸那麼多錢，批評Robinhood允許他承擔過多風險。<br />\n不過，Kearns可能誤解了Robinhood的顯示頁面，實際上Kearns並沒有虧損73萬美元，而是帳戶有1.6萬美元(約12萬港元)，這才是Kearns真正的積蓄。<br />\nRobinhood也證實，Kearns有帳戶，但出於隱私，不會提供任何詳細資料，表示公司所有人都為這消息感難過，目前正審查其選擇權交易產品，以確定是否需要適當的改進。<br />\n<br />\n平台收費都未搞清楚就入場炒槓桿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b0b605c2af5527da86dc59aec6e05dc86d648a","tid":2070641,"uid":83535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"係咪跟左wallstreetbets買YoLo call put<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f2d69e70fc4cc93c1b27911b4a2073de59cf415","tid":2070641,"uid":20368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用都唔識用"},{"pid":"d44ec485b22e70efb1cc93ebac74b89e251b8753","tid":2070641,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Sullimar Capital分析師Bill Brewster日前表示，他的表弟Alexander Kearns是個20歲的大學生 屌那星個分析師做親戚 唔識幫佢睇"},{"pid":"0d14e0a622e34d05716e9e454bfb5acd86c2e47e","tid":2070641,"uid":53433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"而家係咪多左好多學生哥入市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09cd36b939c35c62ccb6d66e06ac2e0086b4d249","tid":2070641,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"媽咪麵都未jump<br />\n點解佢咁快jump<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0078023f53687b58e2d2727d8c0e2625722dbb47","tid":2070641,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ci7kgxF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCi7kgxF.png&h=186bc503&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e94a0b1f52b813024106e6c423a0986e2906495","tid":2070641,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0078023f53687b58e2d2727d8c0e2625722dbb47","tid":2070641,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ci7kgxF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCi7kgxF.png&h=186bc503&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:53:39.000Z","msg":"陰公<br />\n唔識睇咪問人囉⋯⋯"},{"pid":"e4095c55dd5a1777e73d0d45fbe7d77afcc2bb8f","tid":2070641,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"咁佢即係輸幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}